      <header class="section-header">
        <h1 class="section-header__title">Returns</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="rte rte--nomargin">
        <ul>
<li>Returns must be made within 30 days of original purchase.</li>
<li>Returns must be shipped prepaid to the below address with<span> </span><a href="http://www.martinstore.com/shopmartins/Shop%20Martins%20Return%20Form.pdf">return form</a><span>(.pdf format)</span><span> </span>enclosed.</li>
<li>All merchandise must be returned in original, unworn condition with all tags still attached</li>
<li>Credit (less shipping charges) will be issued immediately upon receipt of return.</li>
<li>First time exchanges will be shipped (with no additional shipping charges added) as soon as we receive your return.</li>
<li>Please e-mail us at<span> </span><a href="mailto:sales@shopmartins.com">sales@shopmartins.com</a><span> </span>for availability and we will hold your exchange for you.</li>
<li>All special orders will be subject to a 25% restocking fee.</li>
<li>Gourmet Food &amp; Intimate Apparel may not be returned.</li>
</ul>
<p><span><strong>Returns should be shipped to:</strong><strong><br></strong>Martin's<br>914 N Hervey St<br>Hope AR 71801</span></p>
